		"description": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\">At 7th level your reputation for harshness extends from your allies to your enemies.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\">When you strike an enemy with a melee weapon attack, you can force them to make a Wisdom saving throw with a DC equal to 8 + your proficiency bonus + your charisma modifier.&nbsp;On a failure, they are frightened of you until the end of your next turn.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\">You can do so a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus and regain all expended uses when you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
